scriptname version 0.5

  This module locates the full path to the current script's directory to allow
  the use of of paths relative to the script's directory. Also, it can unshift
  paths relative to the script's directory in @INC.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

Alternatively, to install with Module::Build, you can use the following commands:

	perl Build.PL
	./Build
	./Build test
	./Build install


DEPENDENCIES

None.


